First run tabulatedGenerator to generate .tsv

Then upload to google doc, use google translator, download translated to a .tsv

Then run updaterMain to update english catalog to german
    -- expects to read german-translated-tsv
    -- python updaterMain

That output needs to be manually editied/verified
    -- manually edited file expected to be in JSON format
        -- output of 'jq' has a missing '[]', ','-at-end-of-each-object, ...
        -- therefore those need to be added in manually to make it a valid json

NOTE: 
    Currently we don't use openAI for translation (english-> german). Too many issues in the generated result
    Instead, use google translator

